Open various project-related URLs in your default browser.

Available targets:
  branch  - Open the current branch on GitHub
  issue   - Open the Jira issue linked to the current branch context
  pr      - Open the pull request for the current branch
  repo    - Open the repository homepage on GitHub

Examples:
  # Open the current branch on GitHub
  fotingo open branch

  # Open the Jira issue linked to the current branch context
  fotingo open issue

  # Open the pull request for the current branch
  fotingo open pr

  # Open the repository homepage
  fotingo open repo

  # Get the URL as JSON without opening browser
  fotingo open pr --json

Usage:
  fotingo open [what] [flags]

Flags:
  -h, --help   help for open

Global Flags:
  -b, --branch string   Base branch override (default: auto-detect)
      --debug           Show diagnostic output (includes verbose)
      --json            Output results as JSON
      --no-color        Disable colored output
      --quiet           Suppress non-essential output
  -v, --verbose         Show step-level progress output
  -y, --yes             Accept defaults without prompting
